<paragraph blockId="11.[151,1436,1503,1709]" pageId="11" pageNumber="516">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,617,1540,1565]" pageId="11" pageNumber="516">
Condition of the 
<typeStatus box="[411,475,1540,1565]" pageId="11" pageNumber="516">types</typeStatus>
. 
<typeStatus box="[491,611,1540,1565]" pageId="11" pageNumber="516">Lectotype</typeStatus>
.
</emphasis>
Wings rubbed. Left antenna broken. Midlegs missing. 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1264,1436,1540,1565]" pageId="11" pageNumber="516">
<typeStatus box="[1264,1431,1540,1565]" pageId="11" pageNumber="516">Paralectotype</typeStatus>
.
</emphasis>
Right hindwing with a small tear near apex.
